  <ns0:descriptions>
    <ns0:description descriptionType="Abstract">The PSQL database named &amp;apos;perseus1&amp;apos; was created for an independent research course, Physics 90r, in the fall and winter of 2013. It contains four tables, two of which are used in the accompanying iPython Notebook file. The iPython notebook details the creation of the database, demonstrates the use of the psycopg2 module to query the database, and some visualizations of those queries.</ns0:description>
